description: This Chainlink VRF common Cooter purrs with a rating of 28, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 56, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 1 for East, 1 for South, and 1 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90282-81112-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [56 Votes, Common]
